<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RentOnGo - By Motorq</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400&family=New+Amsterdam&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: "New Amsterdam", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            font-size: x-large;
        }
        body::-webkit-scrollbar{
            display: none;
        }
        nav {
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-right:20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: right;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #000;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav button{
            width: 150px;
            font-family: "New Amsterdam", sans-serif;
            font-size: x-large;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius:10px;
            border:none
        }

        main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section .about{
            height: 100vh; /* Full viewport height */
            padding: 20px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .section {
            height: 100vh; /* Full viewport height */
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .section p{
            align-items: center;
        }

        

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            align-self: start;
        }


        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About Us</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <button ><a href="/login">Login</a></button>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="about" class="section about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>We offer a wide range of cars for rental at competitive prices. Our fleet includes various models to suit all your needs, whether you are looking for a compact car for city driving or a spacious SUV for a family road trip.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="services" class="section">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p>At Car Rental Service, we provide a variety of services to enhance your rental experience. From easy online bookings to flexible rental periods and 24/7 customer support, we strive to make your journey as smooth as possible.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="section">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For inquiries or support, feel free to reach out to us. We are here to help you with all your rental needs.</p>
            <p>Email: info@carrentalservice.com</p>
            <p>Phone: +1 234 567 890</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Car Rental Service. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
